Waxaa sidoo kale la ogaaday in duufaanta cytokine ay sabab u tahay falcelinta difaaca jirka ee dadka qaba SARS iyo MERS.
Xanuunka 'cytokine' waa nooc ka mid ah jawaabta caabuqa ee nidaamsan oo lagu sameeyo iyada oo la sii daayo taxane ah cytokines, oo ay ku jiraan TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ iyo MCP-1.
