Bishii Abriil 10, 2020, Google iyo Apple, shirkadaha maamula barnaamijyada mobilada ee Android iyo iOS, waxay soo saareen aalad ilaalin oo ku saabsan xiriirka, taas oo ay rumeysan yihiin inay ilaalinayso asturnaanta, oo ku saleysan isku-darka Bluetooth Low Energy iyo ilaalinta sirta.
